title: Frequently used Google search terms in Germany 2019
yAxis: Increase of search requests compared to the previous month
summary: The Frequently used Search in the search terms was Search darts_wm , who made 4400 search .
The most used Search was erster_weihnachtsfeiertag , with just 1200 search .

In second place was Search frohes_neues_2020 with 3650 search ; third place went to Search jan_fedder with 4400 search ; fourth place went to Search winteranfang_2019 with 1200 search and fifth place went to Search guten_rutsch , who was 2850 search .
gold: This statistic shows the Google search terms with the highest increase in search volume over the last month in Germany as of January 10 , 2020 . During the period of consideration , search requests containing the term `` Jan Fedder `` increased by 4,400 percent compared to the previous month , while coming in at second place was `` Frohes neues Jahr ( Happy new year ) `` , increasing by 3,650 percent .
